cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper proposes a method for learning physical skills from videos using deep pose estimation and deep reinforcement learning. This involves computer vision techniques (deep pose estimation) and machine learning techniques (deep reinforcement learning) which are commonly associated with the computer vision (cs.CV), robotics (cs.RO), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories of arXiv CS. Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
